		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey,<br /><br />I bought an Enio EXP Board recently because it can allow you to use japanese devises.<br />I would like to plug a japanese controller (player 2 with mic) on it.<br /><br />But so far no luck, I posted few times for helps here and couldn't get any answer. So if any of you has some knowledge about it and willing to share that would clearly make my day.<br /><br />What I did already:<br />-checked the differences between european wiering and colors and checked the Enio scheme to see where and how to connect.<br /><br />I know it sounds pretty simple but it didn't work for me.<br /><br />Any idea?<br />Cheers guys <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />

		

