		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: ENIO EXP Board help for japanese controller</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Reference #1: <a href="http://nesdev.com/Ntd_8bit.jpg" class="postlink">famicom schematic</a><br />Reference #2: <a href="https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/NES_expansion_port_pinout" class="postlink">nesdevwiki:NES expansion port</a><br /><br />Japanese player 2 controller connects to:<br />* Joypad 1 D2 = MIC<br />* Joypad 2 D0 = 4017 D0<br />* out 0 = OUT 0<br />* /OE for joypad 2 = 4017 CUP<br /><br />and don't forget power (Vcc/+5V) and ground (Gnd).

		

